docs.abstract: The Supremes smack down a prehistoric president.

docs.lead_paragraph: There are leaders who are ahead of their times, leaders who are behind their times, and then there’s Donald Trump, who comes from another time altogether. He’s stuck somewhere closer to the Stone Age than to Stonewall. And the Supreme Court just told him so.

docs.abstract: Minneapolis abandoned its vision of an egalitarian society. The region is now paying an enormous price for that choice.
docs.snippet: Minneapolis abandoned its vision of an egalitarian society. The region is now paying an enormous price for that choice.
docs.lead_paragraph: Like many segregated cities before it, Minneapolis is burning. George Floyd’s killing by a police officer is tearing the city and the country apart. But this tragedy is also the result of two Americas, increasingly separate from each other, coming into wrenching conflict.

headline.main: George Floyd and Derek Chauvin Might as Well Have Lived on Different Planets
